{"tid":2408500,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄧炳強︰研不同低殺傷力武器 並稱會盡力堵截煙花來源 強調已充公不少數量","createTime":"2021-02-15T04:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T06:00:12.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fb2d5354767a1bc0bff0434702ed4654b8ef20d8","tid":2408500,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T04:14:48.000Z","msg":"被問警方會否添置電槍 鄧炳強︰研不同低殺傷力武器<br />\n<br />\n警務處處長鄧炳強到長洲視察。他早上乘船抵步後，在警務人員陪同下進入長洲警署，他離開時被問到警方是否會添置電槍，鄧炳強表示正研究很多不同的低殺傷力武器，目的是在真槍以外，有其他降低武力的選擇，包括催淚水槍及胡椒球彈手槍。他強調要安全，同時能提供多一個低武力的選項。<br />\n<br />\n對於農曆年期間本港多處有人違法放炮竹煙花，鄧炳強說會盡力堵截，警方亦已堵截不少炮竹煙花，行動會持續。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575736-20210215.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575736-20210215.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eSq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=f789d763\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575736-20210215.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=dd926c6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575736-20210215.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"8e260ac8434d8425f2bf878ad3d586bd00a57b58","tid":2408500,"uid":127575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T04:15:51.000Z","msg":"即係代表研究緊<span class=\"red\">高</span>殺傷力武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到香港人講廣東話唔講普通話<br />\n莫須有！即刻槍殺"},{"pid":"9457e22d2294471532df2f02819daddbfa402e8c","tid":2408500,"uid":41873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T04:20:31.000Z","msg":"元朗撚到你地話事咩 你地自已都大把生意啦"},{"pid":"d7deb4196c3011ab71a88a0970d89f8fdd0db4b0","tid":2408500,"uid":40415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:45:13.000Z","msg":"警方亦已堵截不少炮竹煙花，農曆新年會在鄧氏宗祠燃點"},{"pid":"1c082b066bec948ae0779ceae0ea8c4dc7039ba5","tid":2408500,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":